FBIS4-50532 "drchi097_a_94011" FBIS-CHI-94-097 Daily Report 19 May 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Conference Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Conference Slovenia's Deputy Premier To Visit OW1905090794 Beijing XINHUA in English 0858 GMT 19 May 94 OW1905090794 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 19 (XINHUA) -- At the invitation of Chinese Vice Premier and Foreign Minister Qian Qichen, Lojze Peterle, deputy prime minister and foreign minister of Slovenia, will pay a visit to China from May 31 to June 5, announced a Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman here today. The spokesman made the announcement at the weekly press conference here this afternoon.
